data.description: The Bungalino is a single-family home (not a townhome) perfectly situated on a corner lot with a covered patio and lots of natural light. Single level with open floor plan perfect for entertaining. 100% energy star certified. This is a 55 and over community in Paramount that is complete and gated with community center, gym and pool and lots of community activities. All lawn care provided. Kitchen features wood floors, alder cabinets, Bosch stainless steel appliances, gas range, pantry, breakfast bar/island, breakfast nook, leathered granite counters and subway tile backsplash. Living room has newer carpet and tray ceilings.  Primary suite features tray ceiling, ceiling fan, walk in closet, dual sinks, quartz counters, tile floors and tile walk in shower. Large laundry room/mud room with tile floors, folding table, cabinets and mud bench. Great location near restaurants and shopping.
